{"tid":570402,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"覺唔覺得夏韶聲danny summer俾人低估得好撚緊要？","createTime":"2018-02-23T15:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T04:51:49.000Z","uid":60015,"like":33,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"da36593c8d0842d3ea0d90c33b3af083baaf2331","tid":570402,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"唔知連登小學生知唔知夏韶聲以前係唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係以為佢淨係識9up外星人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唱過好多經典歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空凳 童年時 結他低泣時 永不放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細細個已經好鐘意聽佢啲歌<br />\n越大越覺得佢地聲好有味道好有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然論唱功未必係超好<br />\n但佢嘅演譯真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次見連登仔講歌手都好似好少提到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多數張學友 e神<br />\n有冇連登老屎忽都鐘意聽danny summer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b0d7564b1d141b52569ca82a3a9cfc8091394d","tid":570402,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76244cc98da10e5b404e1287a4f35db91298db8e","tid":570402,"uid":5652,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"樓誰識野<br />\n張學友 鐘鎮濤 夏韶聲 校長 林子祥 <br />\n其他都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a30d8ebf84c60e1f7fd6ecb1180ff4b6f9a9d7","tid":570402,"uid":5652,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"90後都叫睇過佢拍美味天王<br />\n連登班00後撚識夏韶聲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26820400a2689286a9